Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:19.87,Song,,0,0,0,,If only there were no tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.60,Song,,0,0,0,,School would've been a fun place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:29.94,Song,,0,0,0,,I never cared much for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:38.46,Song,,0,0,0,,I just stared out the window all through class,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.46,0:00:44.50,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)}Always dreaming away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:52.44,Song,,0,0,0,,But if I'd at least taken English seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:59.75,Song,,0,0,0,,By now I'd be some cool international girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.71,0:01:07.32,Song,,0,0,0,,Better to study a little than not at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.99,0:01:12.86,Song,,0,0,0,,There must be at least one thing you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:22.47,Song,,0,0,0,,Better to study while you still have the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:28.11,Song,,0,0,0,,Realizing too late won't help you then.
