Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:38.94,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:47.42,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:55.59,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:23:03.77,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:10.67,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.68,0:23:21.12,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:30.70,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
